#Find number of clusters

wss<-(nrow(Pharms)-1)*sum(apply(Pharms,2,var))
wss
## [1] 180
for(i in 2:15) wss[i] <- sum(kmeans(Pharms,centers = i)$withinss)
wss

## [15]  11.26409
